  schema:name "Eileen Laverty";
  schema:description """With her signature blend of folk, Celtic, and contemporary sounds, Eileen’s music speaks to themes of love, hope, and resilience, resonating deeply with listeners of all ages.

Eileen’s music reflects a broad range of influences and inspiration and is rooted in her love of a good story, but it’s her pure clear voice that is her calling card.""";
