iwts_performer:1050 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Lynn Trefzger";
  schema:description """Lynn's versatile vocal talents bring her many characters to life, including a silly but lovable camel, a grumpy old man, a feisty little girl, and even audience volunteers. Her interactive performances are tailored for family and adult audiences, ensuring a unique and hilarious experience every time.
Over her 30-year career, Lynn has performed worldwide, taking her show to theaters, community events, fundraisers, and aboard the Disney Cruise Lines. She is the recipient of the \"People's Choice Award\" from the Ohio Arts Presenters Association.""";
