iwts_performer:1382 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Jason Bishop";
  schema:description "Internationally acclaimed magician Jason Bishop has headlined two Broadway shows and appeared on NBC, CW, and Europe’s legendary “Le Plus Grand Cabaret du Monde.” Praised by The New York Times for his elegance and precision, Bishop blends cutting-edge illusions, sleight of hand, and sharp wit into a sophisticated performance. His artistry has captivated celebrities and global brands alike—cementing his place as one of magic’s most successful modern illusionists.";
