  schema:name "shameless hussy productions";
  schema:description "With a mandate of \"telling provocative stories about women to inspire the hand that rocks the cradle to rock the world\" Vancouver’s shameless hussy productions puts HERSTORY to the forefront. We search for and create work that provokes a deeper understanding of women's past, present and potential and bring it roaring onto stages across Canada and the US. Currently touring: Love Bomb, our original musical, Dissolve and To Perfection, all by  Canadian playwright, Meghan Gardiner.";
