  schema:name "Darin & Brooke Aldridge";
  schema:description """Darin & Brooke Aldridge have become Grand Ole Opry favorites with over 60 Opry performances and releasing a string of critically acclaimed and commercially successful albums and Number 1 singles.

 Brooke is a four-time consecutive winner of the “Female Vocalist of the Year” for the International Bluegrass Music Association (IBMA). 
 
Their current album, “Talk of the Town” was released in April 2024 and debuted at #1 on the distinguished Billboard Top Bluegrass Album Chart and remained there in the Top 5 for more than 5 weeks.""";
