iwts_performer:2725 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Linda McRae";
  schema:description "Linda McRae is a veteran recording artist and songwriting instructor. From her days with Platinum recording band, Spirit of the West, to everything she's done since, Linda remains an artist full of integrity. Playing banjo, guitar and accordion in a deeply satisfying acoustic style with a big dose of soul and skilled musicality, McRae’s unforgettable melodies and thought-provoking lyrics make her a captivating artist. A BC Entertainment Hall of Fame Pioneer Inductee and a Boston Family Folk Chorale Songwriting Competition winner.";
