iwts_performer:3247 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Matt Zaddy";
  schema:description """Blending folk-rock/rhythm & blues, there’s something for every music fan to love about Matt Zaddy.  A storyteller at heart, Matt’s music speaks to the soul, with tales of life, love, hardship, and redemption.  Having shared stages with K’Naan, Tom Cochrane, Jim Cuddy, The Trews and Cowboy Junkies, Zaddy’s intention is to connect with as many listeners as possible, regardless of genre restrictions. 

Matt’s 2024 single, Far Too Long, was added to over 1000 Spotify Playlists, has radio play in 7 countries, and 63k+ YouTube views.""";
  schema:url <https://www.mattzaddy.com>;
