iwts_performer:3747 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "John Berry";
  schema:description """John Berry is a Grammy Award winning singer/songwriter who has toured professionally at the highest level for more than 30 years. He is a member of the Carolina Music & Entertainment Hall of Fame as well as the North American Country Music Hall of Fame. He performs as a soloist, duo or full band and is famous for his legendary \"Christmas with John Berry\" tour which will enjoy its 29th Anniversary in 2025.

John's music is very well known with the radio hits and songs from films and he leaves audiences wanting more!""";
