  schema:name "Acrobatic Conundrum";
  schema:description "Acrobatic Conundrum, Seattle’s premier contemporary circus arts company, creates ensemble-based performances that amaze and inspire audiences. Founded in 2012 by Artistic Director Terry Crane, the company blends virtuosic circus skill, dance and physical theater to create work that is poetic, a little absurd, and deeply relatable.";
