  schema:name "Lisa Richard";
  schema:description "Lisa Richard is a powerhouse singer-songwriter from Halifax, Nova Scotia, whose soul-stirring vocals blend country, folk, roots, and pop. She’s shared stages with Vince Gill, performed internationally, and earned acclaim for heartfelt songs like “Whiskey Over Me” and “Uniforms (Promises Kept),” making her a rising voice in Canadian music.";
