  schema:name "Jeeyoon Kim";
  schema:description "Award-winning pianist Jeeyoon Kim blends impeccable technique with sensitive artistry to create innovative concert experiences. Her multimedia project si-úm, combining poetry, photography, and music, exemplifies her vision to reimagine classical performance. Beloved by audiences for her warmth and authenticity, she connects deeply from the stage. Jeeyoon has performed at Carnegie Hall and hosts Journey Through Classical Piano.";
