iwts_performer:6294 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Tracy Millar";
  schema:description """As a seasoned and popular artist and musician, Tracy Millar is considered one of Alberta's finest and most talented disciples of traditional country music.
For over two decades, this singer, songwriter, bandleader 
recording artist has shown she is all in for the long run, when it comes to championing her favorite brand of country music.
As a performer who is perfectly at ease singing her unique originals or a country classic tune, Millar's impressive run has been in part, built on her ability to win over fans in any venue and via the airwaves.""";
