iwts_performer:6321 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The CHARMS";
  schema:description """Country Music Alberta 2025 Horizon Group of the Year Nominee, The CHARMS are Husband & Wife duo Meg & Denis Dufresne.  The 2 are celebrated and award winning vocalists and Instrumentalists. 
They have toured the world playing command performances for His Royal Highness, The Prince of Wales, the Saudi Royal Family, the Prince of Monaco, the Duke and Duchess Will and Kate and several Canadian Prime Ministers.
Megan is Western Canada’s Premier Bollywood Violinist and
Denis is 7x CCMA “Musician of the Year” for Fiddle, Mandolin and Banjo""";
