iwts_performer:6399 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Ty Koch";
  schema:description """Emerging singer/songwriter Ty Koch is the type of artist who can seamlessly blend genres; crooner, blues, musical theatre, classical, and every vintage rock song you can think of. His repertoire includes over 50 covers, and a dozen originals.

Ty is also an accomplished touring musician, taking part in two seasons of the Rise Up Reality TV Tours as seen on Roku TV, he has performed with the highly acclaimed British Columbia Boys Choir in over five countries as well as numerous festival appearances under his solo artist name.""";
