  schema:description """Anna Katarina is a Canadian-American singer-songwriter blending retro warmth with indie pop and Americana. Her songs are emotionally honest and hook-driven, shaped by West Coast sensibilities and a love of classic songwriting. Known for her soulful vocals and inviting stage presence, Anna creates music that feels intimate, timeless, and fun.

Anna tours regularly across North America and Europe, building a career rooted in authenticity and connection.""";
