iwts_performer:7345 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Keith Alessi";
  schema:description """Before taking to the stage, Keith was well known as a successful public company CEO, having run companies in both Canada and the US.  He has been a college professor, entrepreneur and has served on numerous corporate and charitable Boards of Directors.

A dual Canadian/US citizen, Keith lives in Meadows of Dan, Virginia. He is a certified public accountant and received his MBA from the University of Michigan, Ann Arbor.

Keith has been touring the show internationally since 2018 across the United States, Canada, the United Kingdom and Scotland.""";
