  schema:description "Inspired by iconic girl groups The Ronettes, The Angels, The Shirelles and The Supremes, The Starlets take you on a musical journey through the 50’s & 60’s when radio was dominated by Pop, Doo-Wop, R&B and Motown. Take a trip back in time as The Starlets perform such memorable hits as My Boyfriend’s Back, Heatwave, These Boots are Made for Walkin’, Be My Baby, Stop! In the Name of Love, and more!";
