  schema:name "ZAY NOVA";
  schema:description "Zay Nova is an Indonesian-born singer-songwriter, radio producer, and TV producer based in St. John's, NL. He released his debut album, Head Above the Water, on January 20th, 2024, and was nominated multiple times at the Music NL Awards, the Canadian Independent Music Video Awards for Best Country Video, the East Coast Music Awards 2025, and ArtsNL’s Emerging Artist of the Year Awards 2025.";
