iwts_performer:8132 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Leanne Lightfoot";
  schema:description """Lightfoot’s raw, honest vocal sound combined with her prowess as a songwriter, melds both joy and sorrow, life lessons, and what she knows best, matters of the heart, call of the land and the bonds that bind one to another.
With upbeat banter and back story, upright bass player Jamie Newsom and guitarist, Jim McLennan add depth and texture to the nuanced collection of songs, where past and present intertwine and where heartache and hope, coexist long after the music fades.""";
