iwts_performer:8143 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Carrie Marshall";
  schema:description "Carrie Marshall is a blend of pop, soul, folk and jazz with singer-songwriter sensibilities.  Known for  expressive, warm vocals, piano-driven melodies, and emotionally rich storytelling, Carrie seamlessly blends styles in her genre-bending shows. Carrie curates several themed shows that resonate with broad audiences, bringing the soul spirit of jazz improvisation to new listeners through popular and original music. Carrie tours with a band ranging from a quintet to an eight-piece ensemble.";
