  schema:description "Canadian Inspirational Country Artist Amanda Hagel has established herself as an artist whose mission is to create music that uplifts, empowers and inspires her listeners. This award winning Saskatchewan native garnered both national and international recognition for her work as a performer and songwriter. With her impressive catalogue of music, great success at Canadian radio & widespread media coverage internationally particularly in the U.S. and South Africa, Amanda has continued to prove herself as an artist on the rise.";
