  schema:name "Jonathon Paterson";
  schema:description "Jonathon Paterson has been working in Canadian theatre for over 30 years as a producer, performer, technician, stage manager, writer, and designer. He has toured internationally and has performed in dozens of theatres and festivals, including the Edmonton Fringe Festival, Just for Laughs, Fringe World (Perth, Aus), and Soho Playhouse (Off-Broadway). Jonathon also has over 2 dozen producing credits and over 25 years experience with his theatre company, RibbitRePublic.";
