iwts_performer:8951 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Maria & Sergei Teleshev  Family Duo Two Accordions";
  schema:description """Maria & Sergei Teleshev, father and daughter, both of them are World Accordion Champions, the winners of International Competitions in the USA, Canada, Australia, Germany, Belarus, Ukraine, Italy, and France.
Maria's recent accomplishments include title \"Prodigy of the Year\", recordings and interviews for NPR's \"From The Top\", Classical King FM, TV news in OR, TX, Jack Kent Cooke Young Artist Award of $10,000 and more. 
Sergei has been performing all over the world since 1995, his popular YouTube channel has received over 6,250,000 views.""";
