iwts_performer:8987 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Alex Zerbe";
  schema:description """Alex Zerbe was born and raised in the Capitol Hill neighborhood of Seattle, WA. His passion for Hacky Sack led him to a 26-year career in the performing arts. 

Alex performs as the Zaniac, at PACs and theaters throughout WA, OR, BC and beyond. He is 2x Guinness World Record holder, a recent college graduate, and has appeared on America’s Got Talent, Last Comic Standing, and CCTV. He was voted Seattle’s Funniest Prop Comedian, and was inducted into the Hacky Sack Hall of Fame in 2023. 

He lives in Olympia, WA with his wife and two daughters.""";
  schema:url <https://AlexZerbe.com>;
