  schema:name "Michelle Calder";
  schema:description "Longtime indie folk-pop singer-songwriter, and emerging recording artist Michelle Calder, from Lower Sackville, Nova Scotia combines her gentle folk-princess vocals with her nature/adventure-themed lyrics and plucky riffs, aiming to entice even the indoorsiest of folks to seek out the wildling within.";
