  schema:description "Ariane Mahrÿke Lemire is a third-generation Western Canadian francophone singer-songwriter whose music spans folk, pop, country, and experimental sounds. Raised in Alberta with Quebec roots, she performs across Canada and internationally, connecting deeply with audiences. With 5 albums, 2 Western Canadian Music Awards, and multiple nominations, Lemire prioritizes storytelling, letting lyrics shape her diverse, boundary-breaking music.";
