iwts_performer:9300 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Miss Emily";
  schema:description """Kingston, Ontario based Miss Emily is celebrating her 21st year as a full-time Soul-Blues-Americana artist.
The 2021 JUNO Nominee & International Songwriting Competition winner won her third  'Female Artist of the Year' at last year's Maple Blues Awards in Toronto.  
Emily is a proud mom and in recent years has been able to tour more extensively, including solo/duo/band performances across Canada, parts of the US, UK & Europe.
Her new album 'The Medicine', produced by Grammy and JUNO Award winning Colin Linden, will be released in October ‘25.""";
