  schema:name "Oh Pray Tell";
  schema:description "Oh Pray Tell is us – Shayna Jones, Sally Titasey and Betty Supple. Three-part harmonies grounded in banjo and stomp-clap-cajon rhythms carry poetry, stories and spoken word. Oh Pray Tell offers up an original, soulful sound influenced by gospel, rhythm & blues, roots music and folk story-telling. ?";
