iwts_performer:9347 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Patti Savard";
  schema:description """Patti Savard is a witty, charismatic comedian whose childlike expressions and sharp humor bring both laughter and heart. She blends small-town warmth with the boldness of a proud queer voice.
She’s performed on some of Canada’s biggest stages, including Toronto’s Massey Hall. In 2024, she was featured in the Seattle International Comedy Competition and made her mark at Vancouver’s Just For Laughs festival in 2025. 
Her one woman show was featured at the 2024 Nanaimo Fringe Fest and will be featured at Vancouver's 2025 Revolver Fest.""";
