iwts_performer:9357 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "JaimesonRhy";
  schema:description """JaimesonRhy are Jaimey Hamilton & Rhyley Bremner
“Blue Cowgirl” New Single out now!
The Duo’s Latest track was Co-written with the talented Dave “Dwave” Thomson (Lady A, Washboard Union) along with Patricia Conroy (Lady A “Need You Now”) The song was also produced by Dave Thomson, in Nashville, TN. Their emotional track is about riding through uncertainty & the fear of running out of time. 2025 was a defiant year for JaimesonRhy performing at major festivals and opening up for Nickelback. Now signed with DECM Management Group, (Toronto).""";
