  schema:description "Ellorie McKnight is a bilingual singer-songwriter and multi-instrumentalist based out of Whitehorse, Yukon. Her songs are shaped by delicate vocals, lyrics painting thoughtful reflections of both the individual and collective human experience, and a nostalgia which invites wonder and dreaming. Whether performing solo or with band, Ellorie’s performance evokes deep emotion and contemplation about relationships, modernity, and what comes next.";
