  schema:name "Dreams2Reality";
  schema:description """Hailing from Vancouver, Canada, Dreams2Reality (DTR) is an acoustic indie rock-pop duo that's been captivating audiences since 2016. With a sound that seamlessly blends passionate lyrics, heartfelt melodies, and an ever-evolving musical style, DTR has quickly become one of the most dynamic acts on the Vancouver music scene.

Comprised of Jonn Epplette (vocals) and Michael Foot (guitars), The duo’s passion for music led them to start revamping cover songs while writing their own original material.""";
