  schema:name "McLeod, Bowman & Bray";
  schema:description """McLeod, Bowman & Bray -  jazz, blues, vintage pop & originals
Cara is a vocalist who continues to push boundaries with an unwavering commitment to connecting with audiences across genres, from opera to jazz. Sean has developed a unique and sought after style, blending jazz & country, which has led him to be regarded as one of Canada’s top guitar players.  Neville's career is a testament to versatility (pianist). Starting as a pipe organist, his journey spans jazz, funk, symphonic, & musical theatre as a pianist, vocalist, producer & performer.""";
