  schema:name "El Balcón";
  schema:description "A festive hurricane, El Balcón captivates and compels their audience with their fiery stage presence, dynamic sound and explosive energy. This Montreal based fully acoustic ensemble is leading a new wave of progressive Latin music. A refreshingly original, East meets West experience with an inspiring sense of groove.";
