iwts_performer:9487 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Ellatric";
  schema:description """Singer/songwriter Ellatric creates and performs eclectic indie folk music.  She strives to expand her artistic boundaries by blurring genres.  Her music uses the language of pure emotion. 
She performs on keyboards and guitar.  Her desire to communicate takes her beyond conventional music venues:  Telluride Bluegrass Festival -Colorado, clubs and conferences including NACA and Soroptomist.
Ellatric has been sponsored by Elixir Strings and received and artist award from Taylor Guitars.  Her music sings of hope 
and her performance is electric.""";
