iwts_performer:9539 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Chantelle Marie";
  schema:description """Edmonton-based singer-songwriter Chantelle Marie, originally from Yellowknife, captivates audiences with soulful performances. Her debut album Butterfly Heard, produced by Stew Kirkwood and released in April 2023, earned airplay on CKUA Radio and features a video for her original song \"Shadows.\"  Chantelle opened for Juno winner Aysanabee, performed at major festivals, and completed a Citadel Theatre musical theatre course.
She's also been featured on international and local radio programs. Butterfly Heard is streaming everywhere.""";
