  schema:name "Hendrika";
  schema:description "Multi-instrumentalist Hendrika is a folk musician from the Yukon. Her love of many genres has led to a versatile and unique collection of original material that pushes the boundaries of modern music in all the right ways - intricate melodies with grounding folk roots, classic rock riffs and soaring vocals will leave you absolutely captivated.";
