iwts_performer:9572 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Marie Flipo-Bergeron";
  schema:description """Singer-songwriter Marie brings a soulful voice with tasteful folk & bluesy sound to your event. Performing mainly as a solo artist, Marie and her acoustic guitar will transport you through original songs, and her renditions of old and newer classics. 

Marie has released her first EP album called Mountains are sleeping giants in June 2024.
 
Marie has opened for  Francophone world renowned artists like Marie-Élaine Thibert and Suzie Villeneuve. She also played in local festivals, restaurants, art gallery and private functions since 2019""";
  schema:url <https://www.instagram.com/marie_flipobergeron?igsh=MWFmamVueXI1NjVmcQ%3D%3D&utm_source=qr>;
