  schema:name "Eliza Mary Doyle";
  schema:description "Bright, feisty, and fierce, this banjo playin’ troubadour is an exceptional teacher, performer, songwriter and non-profit leader. Eliza Mary Doyle is a Juno/International Award winning artist who is “sweet as honey and raw as hide”.  Her discography goes back to 2003, and since, she's recorded on 23 albums, toured Canada, the US, Europe and the UK. High-energy-Bluegrass-Americana.";
