iwts_performer:9615 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Mitchell Stewart Klyne";
  schema:description """My sound is a Country vibe,  with silky smooth type vocal styling.

Born into early Rock n Roll, all styles have influenced my soundtrack of life, particularly music with vocal harmonies. 

Originally a drummer it didn’t take long before I owned a guitar to sing with. 

My music, Easy Listening with Heartfelt Lyrics observing life’s journey.

Presently recording my debut album.
Demos are on Sound Cloud. 

Looking forward to releasing my Music to “The World” or to whoever will kindly give it a whirl.

“Life Starts at 60”Dream Big !!

Cheers""";
