iwts_performer:9650 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Symbio";
  schema:description """The Swedish phenomenon ”Symbio” is regarded as one of the most prominent bands from the progressive Folk & World music scene today. Hearing this symphonic duo will make you doubt the fact that they are only two musicians on stage! Prepare for a mesmerizing, soulful and immersive live experience.

Since 2016 Symbio has toured extensively in more than 20 countries in Europe and North America. The album was awarded ”Best Album of the Year” at the Swedish Folk & World Music Awards 2023.""";
