iwts_performer:9661 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Jen Ambrose";
  schema:description """A little torch and a lot of soul…
A frequent performer throughout the Northwest, Jen Ambrose is seen in a diversity of settings ranging from regional wineries, Casinos and Concerts in the Parks and has opened for a number of well-known artists including  the legendary Ringo Starr & His All Starr Band, hip-hop musician Michael Franti & Spearhead and reggae musicians Pablo Moses and The Norma Frazier Band.  Starr and His All Starr Band,  songstress Dar Williams, Colin Hay (of 80’s band Men at Work) and for 60’s folk/rock legend Donovan.""";
