iwts_performer:9662 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Persona bell";
  schema:description "Persona Bell  studied piano for 11 years at Minneapolis’ McPhail Center for Music. She soon discovered a natural talent for singing, leading her to perform globally as a member of the acclaimed St. Olaf Choir. Throughout a career with performances at the White House, Carnegie Hall, Disney Hall, for the Queen of Norway and China, Persona remains an active performer, singing at weddings and leading cover bands and putting on her own shows.Persona offers private lessons and recently released two singles, Chin Up and Don’t Be Afraid.";
