  schema:description "Billboard Top 10 Blues Artist, 2020 IBC Winner, and JUNO Nominee, Canadian singer/guitarist JW-Jones is known for his high-energy shows! This Maple Blues Award winner also won “Best Guitarist” at the 2020 International Blues Challenge in Memphis, and his latest release, 'Everything Now', is an all-original project with special guest Jimmie Vaughan, and production by Gordie Johnson (Big Sugar). JW has sat in with Buddy Guy eight times, toured with George Thorogood and Robert Cray, and entertained audiences in 24 countries and four continents.";
