  schema:name "Ron Loos";
  schema:description """Ron is an award-winning guitar-slinging singer-songwriter from Saskatchewan, Canada.  

He is a seasoned musical veteran with decades of experience.  His compositions have been included in multiple provincial compilations, and have received local, provincial, and national airplay.  When he performs live, his eclectic and engaging personality really shines. He connects to the crowd with great joy and enthusiasm, and skillfully delivers his unpredictable repertoire of songs!""";
