iwts_performer:9692 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The Imaginaries";
  schema:description """The Imaginaries is an Americana group from OK with husband & wife core duo Shane Henry (guitar/vocals) and Maggie McClure (piano/vocals).  Their music (and acting) can be heard and seen on Amazon Prime, Apple TV, Hallmark, Starz and more. They’ve had over 75 songs placements in film/TV/ads, and released 2 singles in 2024 with Vince Gill and Joe Bonamassa.  Available as a duo or band, their mix of enticing originals & covers is garnering serious industry attention and rave reviews from the public. 
They’re also Guitars 4 Vets Ambassadors.""";
