  schema:name "Emmet Cahill";
  schema:description "Emmet Cahill is a celebrated Irish Tenor known for his rich, emotive voice and captivating performances. A lead singer with Celtic Thunder, he also enjoys a successful solo career including a #1 billboard album and a sold-out Carnegie Hall debut. His versatile repertoire spans Irish classics, broadway hits, and sacred music.";
