iwts_performer:9702 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Lynda Randle";
  schema:description """Traversing a range of genres, singer/songwriter, Lynda Randle is a distinct voice in Christian music. Randle's been honored to share the stage with Rev. Billy Graham, Dr. Tony Evans and Dr. Charles Stanley.

Lynda’s spirituals driven anthology, Pilgrim Journey, made a Top 10 debut on Apple Music’s Top Christian Albums chart. Her latest project, By The Riverside, is a collection of gospel favorites and originals set to the rhythm of acoustic guitars, lively strings and steel guitar.

A peacemaker at heart, Lynda’s music is truly cross cultural.""";
