  schema:name "Dendê & Band";
  schema:description "Celebrated for his infectious energy and masterful command of percussion, Dendê Macedo is a trailblazer in Afro-Brazilian music, blending Bahia’s rich sacred and popular traditions with global influences such as Rumba, Afrobeat and Mbalax to deliver electrifying performances alongside his powerhouse band.";
