iwts_performer:9720 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The Lubben Brothers";
  schema:description """Triplets and high-energy musicians from the farmlands of Iowa and now based in Nashville, Tennessee, The Lubben Brothers have spent the last 15 years pioneering an original sound steeped in lyrical sensitivity, rich vocal harmonies, and the multi-instrumental flair of the American folk tradition.

The Brothers have soloed at venues ranging from South Florida's Meyer Amphitheater and Broward Center for the Performing Arts, to The Gardens Hockey Arena of Northern Minnesota.""";
