  schema:name "Dan Miller's AmeriCoustic Cowboy";
  schema:description "For nearly 20 years, award-winning television host Dan Miller, his daughter Hannah May and Wendy Corr have brought their unique brand of music, humor, western history and poetry to audiences from around the globe. With Dan on lead vocals and guitar, Wendy singing lead and harmony vocals and playing the bass guitar, and Hannah singing and playing fiddle and mandolin, Dan Miller’s AmeriCoustic Cowboy is first-class, wholesome family entertainment.";
