iwts_performer:9758 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Jimmy Hogg";
  schema:description "Jimmy Hogg is a writer, actor, director, comedian and storyteller from Plymouth, UK, who has made his name on the Fringe circuit over the last 20-years with his high-energy, physical, tangential solo shows. Shows include Curriculum Vitae, Figgy Pudding, Like A Virgin, A Brief History of Petty Crime, The Potato King, and Potayto Potahto . Comparisons to Eddie Izzard, Rik Mayall, and John Oliver (and other British people) are frequent if not always accurate or deserved. He has numerous awards and merits and is a 16x BEST OF FRINGE WINNER.";
