iwts_performer:9765 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Danny Drouin";
  schema:description "Danny Drouin is a renowned singer-songwriter from Prince Edward Island, celebrated as a staple in the island's vibrant music scene. With a reputation for exceptional versatility, Danny has made his mark with two solo albums. His talents have been recognized nationally, with two of his songs making the top 100 in the CBC Searchlight competition. He is the recent winner of the inaugural ECCMA Rising Star competition in 2024 in Nova Scotia.  A multi-instrumentalist.  Danny is also known for his skill as a sideman.";
