iwts_performer:9766 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Montgomery Night";
  schema:description """Born at an open jam, Montgomery Night creates something nostalgically new. This five-piece alt rock band, built around principal songwriter Reagan Mae Kuzyk’s powerhouse vocals, hits like a caffeine rush with gritty guitar riffs and flowing piano lines.

Their debut project, the IO EP, marks the beginning of the band's first era showcasing ranging sounds that span from  post-grunge to sentimental love songs. Audiences have praised the band’s diverse style, often walking away feeling like they’ve experienced something unique and genre defining.""";
