  schema:description "Ragamalika Mohanraj is an IT Engineer, Indian Classical dancer, and mother based in Canada.A first-generation South Asian artist, she has been training and performing in Indian Classical dance for over 25 years.Her work bridges tradition and innovation, blending classical techniques with contemporary and intercultural movement.She has performed across major stages in Canada, USA, and India,including the Aga Khan Museum.Recipient of the 2024 North American Tamil Excellence Award,she empowers women artists through dance and cultural storytelling";
