iwts_performer:9777 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Reem Fayyad";
  schema:description """A multifaceted artist and cultural leader, working at the intersection of music, literature, and community building.
My artistic world is where the soul of Arabic music meets a contemporary voice. My practice as a soprano vocalist celebrates and reinterprets Arabic music, from the classics of Fairouz to innovative fusion that bridge musical worlds.
Driven by a mission to enrich my community, I founded the Arab Cultural Club to create a vibrant platform for Arabic and Arabic-inspired art in all its forms.""";
