  schema:name "Youtheatre";
  schema:description """Founded in 1968, Youtheatre is Quebec’s oldest theatre for young audiences (TYA) and the only bilingual TYA company in Canada. 
?Deeply rooted in the 21st century, we explore new theatrical forms, ask challenging questions, tell important stories, and investigate technology’s increasingly contentious role in our lives.
