  schema:name "MOONBEAN";
  schema:description "MOONBEAN is a Toronto-based, hardware electronica duo with lush vocal melodies and flavors of acid-house, techno, disco, and a performance style that serves punk energy and messages of love. Musical inspirations; Peaches, Ladytron and Eurythmics. They've headlined Hillside Festival, Rainbow Trout Festival, Folk On The Rocks, Pride festivals cross-Canada and independently toured Canada-wide twice and Europe three times.";
