iwts_performer:9844 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Firefly Orchestra";
  schema:description """The Firefly Orchestra is a dynamic and innovative ensemble known for its luminous fusion of classical orchestration with modern musical storytelling. Founded with the vision to ignite imagination and wonder through sound, the orchestra draws inspiration from the natural beauty and mystery of the firefly—an emblem of light in darkness. 
With a diverse repertoire spanning contemporary compositions, world music influences, and timeless classics reimagined, the Firefly Orchestra captivates audiences with a rich tapestry of sound.""";
