  schema:name "ACME Time Machine";
  schema:description "ACME Time Machine is the ultimate retro Rock ‘n’ Roll revival band, bringing to life the jukebox hits of the 1950s, '60s and beyond by legendary artists such as Elvis Presley, Ritchie Valens, Buddy Holly, Little Richard, Chuck Berry, The Beatles, Roy Orbison, Sam Cooke and more. Experience the energy and excitement of these songs performed live as you’ve always imagined they could sound!";
