  schema:name "Swiftified: A Taylor Swift Tribute";
  schema:description "Swiftified is a tribute to Taylor Swift, and Taylor’s dynamic catalogue of music packed into a seamless and inclusive music spectacular! You'll hear favorites from every era: Love Story, Wildest Dreams, Cruel Summer, Shake It Off and more! All with a live band and an interactive show that is fun for Swifties of all ages. Come dressed in your favorite era, sparkles and sparkles, and get ready to sing and dance in the aisles! With meet and greet in the lobby after the show ????";
