  schema:description """“Joan Bessie” is the latest project from Singer/songwriter Jessica Beach, whose musical career has spanned the last two decades; showcasing at Canada Music Week, Junofest, The Western Canadian Music Awards and the Reeperbahn festival in Germany.  

