  schema:name "Cody Bolden & The Roadhands";
  schema:description """Cody Bolden and The Roadhands is an Atlanta-based country band currently touring the United States. Their sound combines traditional ballads, classic country, and honky tonk tunes. Their focus is on finding folks that love country music. 

