iwts_performer:9948 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Jim Burke & the Coal Fire Diamonds";
  schema:description """Jim Burke’s voice is gin-soaked, ..a pale-faced Louis Armstrong... and a story of the battle for life and dreams.
Jim performs with his two buddies and they have formed the Coal Fire Diamonds. “My music tends to take on the colors of my surroundings, in the Dominican, I will bring my guitar and jam with the local street musicians, and end up writing a merengue, Cuba a Rhumba. It doesn’t matter what language you speak – everyone understands music. Music is the only truly universal language.”
“Diamonds” is a release of Jim Burke’s original music.""";
  schema:url <https://artists.spotify.com/c/artist/7sLDdIZBakPPlNa2WJR0cY>;
