  schema:name "Paul & the Feels";
  schema:description """Paul & the Feels are a modern soul band with a 70s heart holding nothing back. They're \"all-in from the count-in.\" Fronted by singer-songwriter Paul Fuellbrandt, the Feels mine hope from the grit of the daily grind.

