  schema:name "Lauren Fox";
  schema:description "Lauren Fox's passionate and deeply researched theatrical shows on the music of Joni Mitchell, Leonard Cohen, Laurel Canyon, and rock & roll's groupies of the 60’s and 70’s have played nightclubs, theaters and performing arts centers across the country, as well as London, all to critical acclaim from The New York Times and The Wall Street Journal, among others. She is a MAC, Bistro and Nightlife award recipient.";
