  schema:description "Our show is called The Mysto REALLY BIG Magic Show!  We are exactly that.  We are a big stage illusion show presented in a classic vaudeville style.  Our music is mostly swing and ragtime, our illusion are classic stage illusions presented in our own unique style.  We are good, clean family entertainment.";
