  schema:description "Rebecca Vander Zalm is a New Westminster-based singer/songwriter and performer. She released her debut EP “Baby Steps” in 2025, which was an artistic deep dive into the struggles of adolescence and finding herself. Inspired by innovators like Alanis Morissette and Brandi Carlile, Rebecca shares her most authentic self through her music. She performs with an acoustic guitar and good additude!";
