iwts_performer:9982 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Belle Plaine";
  schema:description """Belle Plaine is a singer/songwriter from Regina. Her work spans Roots, Country, Jazz and Folk. Her new album, The Weather, is produced by Paul Rigby, long time collaborator of Neko Case. In February \"Acting Tough\" was released as its 1st single.

Her 2018 album, Malice, Mercy, Grief + Wrath, received a SMA for Best Album and a JUNO nom. She's toured internationally, notably in Europe in 2019 with Colter Wall. She's performed with symphony orchestras and played festival at Bristol Rhythm & Roots Reunion, Small Halls PEI and Regina Folk Festival.""";
  schema:url <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jEblVqix5jM>;
