iwts_performer:9983 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Kenny Blues Boss Wayne";
  schema:description """KENNY ‘BLUES BOSS’ WAYNE – Piano/Vocals
His many awards include seven Maple Blues Awards (Toronto Blues Society) for ‘piano player of the year ‘and four keyboard awards from Living Blues magazine, in which he was hailed as “an artist bringing the piano back to the front ranks of contemporary Blues.” In 2006 he won a Juno Award for Best Blues Album and was nominated three times afterwards.  In 2017 he was inducted into the Boogie-Woogie Piano Hall of Fame while performing at the Cincy Blues Festival in Cincinnati, Ohio.""";
  schema:url <https://www.kennybluesboss.com>;
