iwts_performer:9990 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The Luckies";
  schema:description "Shari Ulrich. Jeanne Tomie and Hilary Grist teamed up as a very last minute replacement (2 hrs before!) for a mainstage set at MusicFest. Hilary’s IG post following was “One of the most fulfilling musical experiences that I have ever had!! “ and Jeanne and Shari agreed!  All three are veteran artists and songwriters with a love of harmony and songs that hit the mark – with awards and loving fans to show for it. Their show combines piano, guitars, violin, cajon beautiful harmonies, humour and stories from these 3 dynamic women.";
