iwts_performer:10009 a schema:Organization;
  schema:name "Aurore Liang";
  schema:description """urore Liang artiste et ses collaborateurs is a non-profit organization. Since 2018, our mission has been to harmonize traditional Chinese arts with contemporary Western artistic expressions through the creation of interdisciplinary performances and presentations of Beijing Opera.

Our work contributes to the emergence of a more inclusive, equitable, and vibrant society, where every voice resonates within the richness of our shared cultural heritage.""";
