iwts_performer:10025 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Ry Patrick Haint";
  schema:description """?Alt-Country & Canadian Noir
Music for the thinner places in-between.
Returning to the craft with a renewed perspective on the paths we've been granted, Ry Patrick Haint writes alt-country that sits in the shadows and explores the heavy terrain of loss and the quiet sacrifices made in starting over, delivered with the sparse, haunting arrangements of Canadian Noir.
Raised on southern Vancouver Island, his songwriting is a map of a life lived in motion, wonder, regrets, and loss. 
Heart-heavy sounds from underground.""";
  schema:url <https://www.rypatrickhaint.com>;
  schema:knowsAbout <http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/MusicPerformance>;
  schema:genre "Folk/Bluegrass/Americana";
