iwts_performer:10031 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Michaela Slinger";
  schema:description """Michaela Slinger is a legendary songbird-in-the-making (Dan Mangan). Her EP THERE’S STiLL TiME YET and forthcoming LP GREEN AND TRYiNG were recorded with David Vertesi (Haley Blais, Hey Ocean!) and Jonathan Anderson (Ocie Elliott, Field Guide). She has opened for Dermot Kennedy and Donovan Woods.

Her sophomore record This Can’t Last Forever (604 Records) received praise from CBC Music and The Georgia Straight and led to her nomination for Pop Artist of the Year at the 2024 Western Canadian Music Awards.""";
