  schema:name "re:Naissance";
  schema:description """re:Naissance is a boundary-defying collective of creators who craft immersive worlds through boundless storytelling, engaging audiences in transformative experiences that challenge and expand the possibilities of live performance. 

We are the creators of the internationally award-winning trilogy: Orpheus VR, Live from the Underworld and Eurydice Fragments and the chart topping sci-fi, podcast, The Apocrypha Chronicles.""";
